snippet.title: Miss Rosen's Wowtastic! Marching Band – Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
The band is in town, and it’s time for some fun! Join Miss Rosen, a clockwork majorette escaped from her music box, as she travels the world solving mind-bending puzzles that’ll test your luggage-packing skills to the max!

Miss Rosen's Wowtastic! Marching Band will release for the Nintendo Switch on October 10th, 2024.
